message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance, my name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm happy to chat with you today. I need some help with my car insurance policy.
Of course, I'm here to assist you with that. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security?
Sure! My full name is Sarah Johnson.
Great, thank you for completing security. How can I help you with your car insurance policy today?
I recently had an accident and need to make a claim. Can you help me with the process?

I'm deeply sorry to hear about your accident. Let me see what we can do to assist you. One possible resolution could be starting the claim process for you. Can you confirm your date of birth for additional checks?
Thank you for providing that information. We've agreed to start the claim process for you. I'll need to gather some details, can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
Yes, my address is 123 Oak Street, London, NW10 6RF.
That's all sorted. To proceed with the claim, could you please confirm your email address?
Thank you for completing security. I have all the details needed to assist you with the claim. I'll get started on this right away.
Thank you so much, Chris. I really appreciate your help!
You are welcome, Sarah. I'm glad that I was able to help. Please allow 2-3 business days for the claim process to be initiated. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's all for now. Thank you again for your help, Chris. Have a great day!
You're welcome, Sarah. I hope everything goes smoothly with your claim. Have a wonderful day too!
